ithering-by-Sea'' || [[ABC Books]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2014\"/>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20142|[[2014 in literature|2014]]}} || {{sortname|Lian|Tanner}} || ''Sunker's Deep'' || [[Allen & Unwin]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2014\"/>\n\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20151|[[2015 in literature|2015]]}} || {{sortname|Meg|McKinlay}}* || ''{{sort|Single Stone|A Single Stone}}'' || [[Walker Books Australia]] || <ref name=\"AAW 2015\">{{citation | title = The Winners of the 2015 Aurealis Awards |url=https://aurealisawards.org/2016/03/25/the-winners-of-the-2015-aurealis-awards/| publisher = WASFF | date = 2016-03-25 | accessdate = 2016-03-25}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20152|[[2015 in literature|2015]]}} || {{sortname|Angelica|Banks}} || ''{{sort|Week Without Tuesday|A Week Without Tuesday}}'' || [[Allen & Unwin]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2015\">{{citation | title = ANNOUNCEMENT: 2015 Aurealis Awards Shortlists |url=http://aurealisawards.org/2016/02/17/announcement-2015-aurealis-awards-shortlist/| publisher = WASFF | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-03-14}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20152|[[2015 in literature|2015]]}} || {{sortname|Jack|Heath}} || ''{{sort|Cut-Out|The Cut-Out}}'' || [[Allen & Unwin]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2015\"/>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20152|[[2015 in literature|2015]]}} || {{sortname|Meg|McKinlay}} || ''Bella and the Wandering House'' || [[Fremantle Press]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2015\"/>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20152|[[2015 in literature|2015]]}} || {{sortname|A. L.|Tait}} || ''{{sort|Mapmaker Chronicles: Prisoner of the Black Hawk|The Mapmaker Chronicles: Prisoner of the Black Hawk}}'' || [[Hachette Australia]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2015\"/>\n\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20161|[[2016 in literature|2016]]}} || {{sortname|Kim|Kane}}* || ''When the Lyrebird Calls'' || [[Allen & Unwin]] || <ref name=\"AAF 2016\"/><ref name=\"AAW 2016\">{{citation | title = Announcing 