] season.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Thoren |first1=Petra |title=Football stand ready for West Ham |url=https://www.aftonbladet.se/sportbladet/fotboll/a/awdxOd/fotbollstalangen-klar-for-west-ham |accessdate=22 March 2020 |work=Sport Bladet |date=3 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=\"Very sick - you are dead at the end of the day\" |url=https://www.expressen.se/sport/fotboll/sjukt-mycket-man-ar-dod-i-slutet-av-dagen/ |accessdate=22 March 2020 |work=Expressen |date=29 January 2020}}</ref> Of the signing, manager [[Matt Beard]] noted, \"Filippa is a talented and pacey full-back who has already shown her quality, despite her young age, in Swedish football.\"<ref name=\"vavel_040120\"/>\n\n===International===\nWallen represented Sweden on the [[Sweden women's national under-17 football team|under-17 national team]].<ref name=\"vavel_040120\">{{cite news |last1=Reis |first1=Bruna |title=West Ham Transfer News:  Women's team confirm the signing of defender Filippa Wall\u00e9n. |url=https://www.vavel.com/en/football/2020/01/04/womens-football/1008575-west-ham-transfer-news-womens-team-confirm-the-signing-of-defender-filippa-wallen.html |accessdate=22 March 2020 |work=Vavel |date=4 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{soccerway|filippa-wallen/436785/}}\n* [https://www.whufc.com/teams/women/squad/filippa-wallen West Ham United player profile]\n* [https://www2.svenskfotboll.se/landslag/landslagsdatabas/landslagsspelare/?fplid=5b9078fd-93fc-49a2-884f-d3d98978d231 Sweden player profile] {{in lang|sv}}\n\n{{West Ham United W.F.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Wallen, Filippa}}\n[[Category:2000 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Swedish women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Damallsvenskan players]]\n[[Category:West Ham United F.C. Women players]]\n[[Category:IF Brommapojkarna players]]\n[[Category:AIK Fotboll (women) players]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Swedish expatriate footballers]